 and decrease in m 1 because the higher the (money made/good thing received) of a 
 crop, the greater the amount of land gave out to it. 
 This ratio is also expected to decrease in vkk and 
 increase in v 11 because for (not wanting to do anything dangerous) people 
 the higher the variance of a crop, the smaller the 
 amount of land gave out to it. Table 1 shows the 
 results of the four instrumentallogit (moving backwards). Out 
 of 16 signs, only one has a significant opposite sign. 
